 instinct to freeze or follow\u2014exactly the wrong instinct in an active shooter situation\u2014is replaced with response-ready reactions that are then second-nature in a time of crisis.", "short_description": "Active Shooter Survival is an Immersive Training for users to practice how to protect themselves in the event of an active shooter situation."}]}, "developer_name": null, "developer_privacy_policy_url": "https://incitevr.com/more/privacy-policy", "developer_terms_of_service_url": null, "publisher_name": "inciteVR", "support_website_url": null, "website_url": "https://www.incitevr.com/more/active-shooter", "category": "APPS", "comfort_rating": "NOT_RATED", "comfort_tags": [], "context_category": {"id": "362692211442873", "context_category": "APPS"}, "context_topics": [{"id": "514087707868786"}, {"id": "1043107547362485"}], "external_subscription_type": "NOT_REQUIRED", "genres": ["EDUCATIONAL", "SIMULATION"], "has_in_app_ads": false, "internet_connection": "REQUIRED", "play_area": "MOVEMENT", "recommended_graphics": null, "recommended_memory_gb": null, "recommended_processor": null, "supported_in_app_languages": ["en"], "supported_input_devices": ["OCULUS_TOUCH"], "supported_player_modes": ["STANDING", "ROOM_SCALE"], "supported_tracking_modes": [], "user_interaction_modes": ["SINGLE_USER"], "id": "7478230545555119"}, "review_messages": [""]}]}, "cover_square_image": {"uri": "https://scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com/v/t64.5771-25/39031613_202629611663542_9193379423895575644_n.png?stp=dst-png_s360x360&_nc_cat=107&ccb=1-7&_nc_sid=6e7a0a&_nc_ohc=djxCNjATMHwQ7kNvgEFTH4m&_nc_zt=3&_nc_ht=scontent-iad3-1.oculuscdn.com&oh=00_AYBAR1cSKfJYjWedJH7RQvgeEU1UcFCQYbkfKpyODXyEWw&oe=674DB4CC"}, "is_concept": false, "is_test": false, "is_trial_offer_valid": false, "display_name": "Active Shooter Survival", "platform": "ANDROID_6DOF", "context_category": {"context_category": "APPS", "id": "362692211442873"}, "context_topics": [{"topic_name": "Hands-On Training", "id": "514087707868